<paragraph id="8BCA3687FFDAFFD6FF6CFB13162CC7A8" blockId="13.[164,779,1181,1264]" pageId="13" pageNumber="710">
<emphasis id="B901EA95FFDAFFD6FF6CFB131669C7EA" box="[164,290,1181,1202]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="710">Etymology:</emphasis>
The name 
<taxonomicName id="4C754D04FFDAFFD6FE72FB101541C7EB" authorityName="Rotheray &amp; Marcos-García &amp; Hancock &amp; Pérez-Bañón &amp; Maier" authorityYear="2009" box="[442,522,1182,1203]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Copestylum" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="710" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="tetetzoi">
<emphasis id="B901EA95FFDAFFD6FE72FB101541C7EB" box="[442,522,1182,1203]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="710">tetetzoi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
refers to the cactus species 
<taxonomicName id="4C754D04FFDAFFD6FEC9FB32154AC789" authorityName="Backeberg" authorityYear="1938" baseAuthorityName="F. A. C. Weber" box="[257,513,1212,1233]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Cactaceae" genus="Neobuxbaumia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="13" pageNumber="710" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="tetetzo">
<emphasis id="B901EA95FFDAFFD6FEC9FB32154AC789" box="[257,513,1212,1233]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="710">Neobuxbaumia tetetzo</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from which the 
<typeStatus id="54CE8825FFDAFFD6FD1BFB32179EC7A8" pageId="13" pageNumber="710">holotype</typeStatus>
was reared.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BCA3687FFDAFFD6FF6CFA94151DC57C" blockId="13.[164,779,1305,1572]" pageId="13" pageNumber="710">
<emphasis id="B901EA95FFDAFFD6FF6CFA941626C677" box="[164,365,1306,1327]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="710">Taxonomic notes:</emphasis>
The adult of this species can be easily separated from other Marginatum group adults by the male genitalia, black frons, and wings hyaline without brown spots. The larva and puparium of 
<taxonomicName id="4C754D04FFDAFFD6FD3AFAF817BFC6F1" authorityName="Rotheray &amp; Marcos-García &amp; Hancock &amp; Pérez-Bañón &amp; Maier" authorityYear="2009" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Copestylum" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="710" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="tetetzoi">
<emphasis id="B901EA95FFDAFFD6FD3AFAF817BFC6F1" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="710">C. tetetzoi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is similar to 
<taxonomicName id="4C754D04FFDAFFD6FE68FA1A1564C6F1" authorityName="Curran" authorityYear="1930" box="[416,559,1428,1449]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Copestylum" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="710" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bequaerti">
<emphasis id="B901EA95FFDAFFD6FE68FA1A1564C6F1" box="[416,559,1428,1449]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="710">C. bequaerti</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="4C754D04FFDAFFD6FDBBFA1A15A3C6F1" baseAuthorityName="Williston" baseAuthorityYear="1887" box="[627,744,1428,1449]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Copestylum" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="710" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="lentum">
<emphasis id="B901EA95FFDAFFD6FDBBFA1A15A3C6F1" box="[627,744,1428,1449]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="710">C. lentum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in having an AP which is shorter than the width of the TR. The nontapering punctured AP separate 
<taxonomicName id="4C754D04FFDAFFD6FD79FA5F178FC55D" authorityName="Rotheray &amp; Marcos-García &amp; Hancock &amp; Pérez-Bañón &amp; Maier" authorityYear="2009" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Copestylum" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="710" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="tetetzoi">
<emphasis id="B901EA95FFDAFFD6FD79FA5F178FC55D" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="710">C. tetetzoi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from 
<taxonomicName id="4C754D04FFDAFFD6FED8FA7E16C8C55D" baseAuthorityName="Williston" baseAuthorityYear="1887" box="[272,387,1520,1541]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Copestylum" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="710" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="lentum">
<emphasis id="B901EA95FFDAFFD6FED8FA7E16C8C55D" box="[272,387,1520,1541]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="710">C. lentum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and the absence of anterior spiracles separates it from 
<taxonomicName id="4C754D04FFDAFFD6FE0AF9801504C57B" authorityName="Curran" authorityYear="1930" box="[450,591,1550,1571]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Copestylum" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="710" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bequaerti">
<emphasis id="B901EA95FFDAFFD6FE0AF9801504C57B" box="[450,591,1550,1571]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="710">C. bequaerti</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
